You can easily create:
Total Call Duration = Day + Eve + Night minutes
Complaint Flag = Customer Service Calls > 3
Recharge Frequency (can be derived if transaction data exists)

Added the total call duration in the with these 

Example (Common Format)

If:
Day Minutes → Column F
Evening Minutes → Column G
Night Minutes → Column H
Then in Column I (Total Call Duration) enter:
=F2+G2+H2


Complaint Flag = Customer Service Calls > 3
If Customer Service Calls is in column C, then in row 2 enter:
=IF(C2>3,"1","0")

# What This Does:
If Customer Service Calls > 3 → Yes  0r "1" as (High complaints)  1 = High Complaint Customer
If ≤ 3 → No or "0" (Normal level) 0 = Normal Customer
